                        <label>‡πÑ‡∏°‡πâ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°:</label>
                        <input type="number" class="range-start" value="1" min="1">
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <label>‡πÑ‡∏°‡πâ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏™‡∏¥‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏™‡∏∏‡∏î:</label>
                        <input type="number" class="range-end" value="100" min="1">
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <label>‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏¢‡∏∞‡∏´‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á (‡∏à‡∏∏‡∏î):</label>
                        <input type="number" class="range-distance" value="300" step="100" min="100">
